7 SUMMARY
128 Public Law 2023, chapter 643, Part KKKK, section 3 established an eviction
139 prevention pilot program within the Maine State Housing Authority. This bill establishes
1140 the Maine Eviction Prevention Program as a permanent program within the authority and
1151 provides funding for the program.
